<p><b>P.S.</b> Quick Italian lesson for you! 🇮🇹</p>

<ul>
	<li><b>Salute</b> (sah-LOO-teh) = What you say when toasting, like "cheers!"</li>
	<li><b>Grazie</b> (GRAHT-tsee-eh) = Thank you! (Don’t forget the “eh” at the end 😉)</li>
</ul>

<p>Now you’re basically fluent! 😆</p>

